{
    "version": 6,
    "bundle": "C3HH6IOXFNVK5JOR6CUKFUIWETKQPGHV",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041129003",
    "title": "潰れるほどに眩しくとも",
    "enTitle": "Radiance Overwhelming",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "わたしの、勝ちよ！",
            "enText": "It's my victory!",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -6207923643860845047
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 414238223021610191,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "高らかな宣言が、しん、と静まり返った異国のターフに響く。\n――ぞくりと肌が粟立ち、胸の奥が震えた。",
            "enText": "Her loud declaration echoes across the turf in a foreign land. \n――I could feel goosebumps as her cry reverberated through my body.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": -1541076897708184731
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8507938773716965376,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "勝ちたいウマ娘がいるんです。\n海外を拠点にしているから、彼女のホームまで行きたいのですが――",
            "enText": "There's an Uma Musume that I want to win against. She's based \noverseas, so I'd like to visit her on her home turf, but――",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 256,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 22,
                    "pathId": -3429128161152834524
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 321,
                    "pathId": 4001655253023095380
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 236,
                    "pathId": 5322302496463377256
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 298,
                    "pathId": -874560266941143045
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2596051215596791637,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "学園のルール上、生徒ひとりでは渡航許可が下りないんです。\n親族や教官に都合がつく方がおらず……それで、貴方ならば、と。",
            "enText": "According to the academy rules, students will not \nreceive permission if they travel alone. My family and \ninstructors will be unavailable……So I thought I'd ask you.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 362,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "なるほど……",
                    "enText": "I see……",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 379,
                    "pathId": 5689944440315718041
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 8991253237693032743
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 412,
                    "pathId": -7323748573209799983
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8331256425643038327,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "無茶な頼みであることはわかっています。\nきちんと話したのは、あの日の一度だけですから。",
            "enText": "I know that I'm asking for a lot, since the \nonly time we talked was that one time back then.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 213,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 261,
                    "pathId": -5019053226254644044
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 4958086437569372409
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 419,
                    "pathId": 2097544180102910865
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7386772461022624348,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "でも、お願いします！\nわたし、どうしてもあの子に勝ちたいんです！",
            "enText": "But, please! I really want to win \nagainst that girl, no matter what!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 207,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": -491320155772262368
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -5317698217347460922
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 412,
                    "pathId": 7542650242864619766
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3615892292856850531,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そのことはよく、知っていた。\nけれどまさか本当に、海外へ渡ってまで成そうとするとは……。",
            "enText": "I was already well aware of that. \nBut I didn't think she'd go so far as to travel overseas for it……",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 168,
                    "pathId": -1542832927855431544
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 412,
                    "pathId": -2317331700092789580
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7747590358281923792,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "いったいその執念で、どこまで成し遂げてしまうのだろう――\nそう思ううち、気づけば……応えていた。",
            "enText": "With that kind of determination, just how much \ncould she achieve? As I was giving that some \nthought, I realized……I already had my answer.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "――わかった、俺が付き添うよ",
                    "enText": "――Got it. I'll go with you",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "――わかった、私が付き添うよ",
                    "enText": "――Got it. I'll go with you",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 168,
                    "pathId": -1553298131988582079
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 412,
                    "pathId": 1246110705640813570
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1752668883523001444,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……！　ありがとうございます！\nそれでは……また詳細が決まり次第、お伝えしにきます。",
            "enText": "……! Thank you very much! \nThen……once all the particulars are figured out, I'll let you know.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 248,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……トレーニングの、サポートもしようか？",
                    "enText": "……Do you want training support too?",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 184,
                    "pathId": -3421739233244867248
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 3600393750371612463
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": -265637777549624324
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5625832872181629995,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "え……っ、本当、ですか？\nありがとうございます、とっても助かります！",
            "enText": "Eh……do you mean it? \nThank you very much, it would be really helpful!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 219,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -7466961320378668912
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 8475796498404367541
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2814838192842780472,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "計測なりなんなり、手伝えることはありそうだ。\nこうして、海外でのリベンジに向け共に駆け抜ける日々が始まった！",
            "enText": "There were probably all kinds of things I could help \nwith, like recording times and such. And so we began \nworking together towards her overseas revenge match!",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 134,
                    "pathId": -7606624437656837984
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 170,
                    "pathId": -7282511543893510065
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8572717837035392930,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "はあ、はあ、はぁ……。ずいぶん遠くまで来てしまいましたね。\nバイクの燃料は、大丈夫ですか？",
            "enText": "Haa, haa, haa…… Looks like we've come pretty far. \nHow's the bike's fuel, still fine?",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 339,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "こちらは大丈夫だけど――君こそ",
                    "enText": "The bike's fine――what about you?",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "こちらは大丈夫だけど――貴方こそ",
                    "enText": "The bike's fine――what about you?",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 200,
                    "pathId": 8852103217122600963
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 90,
                    "pathId": -7853293332889764302
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": -7354576310675868339
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": -5755400788696028001
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -995146037305155764,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "アーモンドアイは、森や丘、山道などの起伏のある\n不整地を、ほとんど休むことなく走り続けていた。",
            "enText": "Almond Eye had just run, nonstop, over rough \nterrain through forests, hills, and mountain paths.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 200,
                    "pathId": -9154714994698634053
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 173,
                    "pathId": -3723236477322349606
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8063827415737222630,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "無理するくらいがいいんです、持久力をつけたいので。\n前回、最終直線で突き放されましたから。",
            "enText": "It's better to push myself, so I can build up endurance. \nThat time, on the final straight, they got away from me, after all.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 285,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 297,
                    "pathId": 3187083786519647243
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": -1499898901061968261
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4337719997870193479,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ただでさえ、向こうの芝は重いですし。そのためには\n自分のリズムを維持できるだけの心肺機能を手に入れなきゃ。",
            "enText": "The turf over there is heavier. \nSo I need to be able to keep my rhythm and work on my cardio.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 279,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 301,
                    "pathId": 1342282358811920840
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 370,
                    "pathId": -5375822561159527525
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5836810912238865394,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……と、降ってきましたね。",
            "enText": "……Oh, looks like it's starting to rain.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 138,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": -6004189480965013032
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": -7929120467763670880
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2402226339072935146,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "――冷たくて、気持ちいい。",
            "enText": "――It's cold, and feels really good.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 176,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ちょうどいい、一度休もうか",
                    "enText": "Perfect, let's take a quick break then",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 228,
                    "pathId": -6560681548607435611
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 218,
                    "pathId": 6442023263250545514
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1955598297047811412,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "いえ、時間がもったいないので！　……あっ、\nトレーナーさんは帰っていて下さいね！　お疲れさまでした！",
            "enText": "No, I don't want to waste any time! ……Ah, Trainer-san, \nyou can go ahead and head back! Good work out there!",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 284,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 267,
                    "pathId": 4828282734255411963
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 1721195204313917958
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -716653048936935671,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "躊躇いなく飛び出して、\n大粒の雨の中、彼女はさらにさらに、加速していく――",
            "enText": "She dashed away without hesitation, \naccelerating off in to the pouring rain――",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（俺にも……何かできることはないか）",
                    "enText": "(Is there……anything else I can do?)",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "（私にも……何かできることはないかな）",
                    "enText": "(Is there……anything else I can do?)",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": 4365129764495477743
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8040891934045361032,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "レース教本を広げ、計測結果を並べる。\n彼女に許可をもらい録ったフォームをコマ送りで何度も再生する。",
            "enText": "I started looking over the racing manuals and her \nrecorded data. With her permission, I recorded her \nform on video and was reviewing it now, frame by frame.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -6396132823451583497,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "呼吸の仕方、可動域の幅、腕の振り。彼女にとって\n理想的なフォームを作れれば、きっと強さを後押しできる。",
            "enText": "Her breathing, range of motion, arm swinging. If she could adjust \nher form to more ideally fit her, it would surely make her stronger.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 5978124728084449926,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "気づけば日は昇っていて――",
            "enText": "Before I realized it, the sun was already rising――",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（……今日のトレーニングは夕方から、か）",
                    "enText": "(She'll be training in the evening)",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4064411446391059020,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "タイムリミットは残り約12時間。\n落ちる瞼をこすり、微調整のため再度机に向かった。",
            "enText": "Probably not for another 12 hours or so. \nI rubbed my eyes and went back to my desk to make some revisions.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 1124361839849316177,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "これって――",
            "enText": "This is――",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 37,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "君にとっての理想的なフォームだ",
                    "enText": "This is the form that works best for you",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "貴方にとっての理想的なフォームだよ",
                    "enText": "This is the form that works best for you",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 123,
                    "pathId": 1504578210682881290
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5065572745689303724,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ありがとうございます！　さっそく試してみますね。\nこっちは……、フォームのためのウエイトトレーニングですか。",
            "enText": "Thank you very much! I'm going to try it out immediately, okay? \nAnd this is……weight training meant to work with this form.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 314,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 222,
                    "pathId": 8613697437533133408
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 7335977260466417213
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2941303188345145884,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……？\n……あの。このファイル、『ver.1』と、あるのですが――",
            "enText": "……? \n……Um. This file says 『ver.1』 on it though――",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 208,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 236,
                    "pathId": -4302005056689231910
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 206,
                    "pathId": 3560317102104087741
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6631234880907070799,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "慌てて確認すると、確かに。\n間違えて最初に組んだ不完全なものを見せてしまっていた。",
            "enText": "I took a quick look, and sure enough, it did. \nI accidentally showed her my first draft.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "悪い、本物はこっちなんだ",
                    "enText": "Sorry, this is the one it should be",
                    "nextBlock": 28
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ごめん、本物はこっちなの",
                    "enText": "Sorry, this is the one it should be",
                    "nextBlock": 28
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 182,
                    "pathId": 5033695006332253162
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 7331007483330225714
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8622924752424255570,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "『ver.9』――\nあぁ！　こことここと……ここの数値も違いますね……へぇ……。",
            "enText": "『ver.9』――Ohh! Here and here……and here. \nThe numbers are different……Ohhhh……",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 339,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 181,
                    "pathId": -3668684770008654251
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8554590431726853960,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――無事、一助となれただろうか。\nともかくその後も、獅子奮迅のトレーニングの日々は続いた！",
            "enText": "――I really hope it's helpful for her. \nAt any rate, we continued to train tirelessly after that!",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 181,
                    "pathId": 6756544293449550649
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6909788673546095749,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "――ッ！！\nまだまだっ、まだまだっ、まだまだぁ！！！",
            "enText": "――!! \nNot yet not yet, not yet not yet, not yet noooot yeeeet!!!",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 166,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -7136722801632185121
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7779705581154324198,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
