        },
        {
            "jpName": "海外ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Overseas Uma Musume",
            "jpText": "Welcome to my turf! You ready to run?\n（ようこそ、我がホームへ。調子はいいかい？）",
            "enText": "Welcome to my turf! You ready to run?",
