            "pathId": 4388064116307670061,
            "blockIdx": 36
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……『わざわざ日本から？』『デビュー前の子でしょ、無茶だよ』\nそんな囁きが、ちらほらと集まったウマ娘から聞こえる中――",
            "enText": "……『All the way from Japan?』『For a pre-debut girl, that's crazy』 \nThose were the whispered words of the other gathered Uma Musume――",
            "nextBlock": 38,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": 411318142680378261
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 904287535034540431,
            "blockIdx": 37
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ついに、3度目のリベンジマッチが幕を開けた！",
            "enText": "Finally, her third revenge match had started!",
            "nextBlock": 39,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
