            "pathId": 6599690448106509817,
            "blockIdx": 54
        },
        {
            "jpName": "幼いアイ",
            "enName": "Young Ai",
            "jpText": "次は絶対、わたしが勝つもん……っ！",
            "enText": "Next time, I'll win for sure……!",
            "nextBlock": 56,
            "origClipLength": 100,
            "voiceIdx": 34,
            "pathId": 7576125769364655436,
            "blockIdx": 55
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "体格差があっても。年上の子が相手でも。指導の先生にだって\n負けたら悔しくて、だからその分、たくさんたくさん鍛えて――",
            "enText": "Even if there was a difference in height. Even against \nolder girls. Even losing against my instructors would be \nfrustrating. And because of that, I'd train and train so much――",
            "nextBlock": 57,
            "origClipLength": 374,
            "voiceIdx": 35,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 140,
                    "pathId": 550377351693363520
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 188,
                    "pathId": -3976977704187057225
                }
