            "pathId": -3123283010868801984,
            "blockIdx": 56
        },
        {
            "jpName": "幼いアイ",
            "enName": "Young Ai",
            "jpText": "はあ！　はあ！　頭、ふらふら……！\n……でもまだ、まだまだっ！　これじゃ勝てないっ！　たああ！！",
            "enText": "Haa! haa! My head……is spinning……! \n……But not yet, not yet not yet! I can't win like this! Taaa!!",
            "nextBlock": 58,
            "origClipLength": 375,
            "voiceIdx": 36,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": -778267974837068744
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": 4048541222583308868
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3734629563824747615,
            "blockIdx": 57
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "――そうして、全部に勝ってきました。",
            "enText": "――And so, I ended up winning against all of them.",
            "nextBlock": 59,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": 37,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": 5687520189023302948
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": -5071420654097891335
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3203951597890162707,
            "blockIdx": 58
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "頑張って勝てたら嬉しくって。\nもっと、もっともっと勝ちたいって気持ちが膨らむんです！",
            "enText": "Working so hard and winning made me so happy. And that feeling \nof wanting to win just kept growing and growing and growing!",
            "nextBlock": 60,
            "origClipLength": 226,
            "voiceIdx": 38,
            "animData": [
