            "pathId": 8335816385095194341,
            "blockIdx": 59
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "――わたし、勝つことが好きなんです。世界でいちばん！",
            "enText": "――I love winning. More than anyone else in the world!",
            "nextBlock": 61,
            "origClipLength": 162,
            "voiceIdx": 39,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 147,
                    "pathId": 2956093582625164819
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -3685790708118778491
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5814225439107224014,
            "blockIdx": 60
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――背筋が、つ、と冷える感覚。",
            "enText": "――I felt a sudden chill.",
            "nextBlock": 62,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 120,
                    "pathId": 6787884559000245885
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2484267298139357834,
            "blockIdx": 61
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "理解できたと思っていた存在は――彼女ではなかった。\nすぐそこにいるのに、遠くにいるような、そして、なぜか。",
            "enText": "I thought I understood her――but it had only been surface level. \nShe was right there, yet still felt so far away. But for some reason――",
            "nextBlock": 63,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 139,
                    "pathId": 3192685167496168508
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8637720604712485571,
            "blockIdx": 62
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "ですが――\nそれを果たしうるウマ娘ならば、自然と知っているのでしょう。",
            "enText": "However――When an Uma Musume that can achieve \nthat appears, I'm sure all eyes will be on her.",
            "nextBlock": 64,
            "origClipLength": 205,
            "voiceIdx": 40,
            "animData": [
